description: Neema's is a southern comfort food trailer serving everything delicious in Seattle. The food is based on southeastern coastal cuisine, America's original fusion food. Comprised of a mixture of Africa, European and Native American ingredients and techniques, the food ranges from barbeque to seafood including traditional sides and the unconventional. Neema's food is fresh daily from the ribs to the bread! Their goal? To give customers a positive experience, delight the taste buds and fill those stomachs!
name: Neema's Comfort
